{
  "chapter": 31,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十一回 误失贞。芮玮在摩霄峰练成大龙剑后，准备下山前往点苍山寻找高莫野。林琼菊因芮玮不先送她回黑堡而生气，拒绝传授伤心剑。芮玮一怒之下下山，但半途折返，两人和好。当夜有人假冒芮玮与林琼菊发生关系，林琼菊误以为是芮玮。次日芮玮返回，林琼菊告知失身之事，芮玮意识到那晚出现的是简召舞而非自己。本章揭示了林琼菊对芮玮的深情，以及简召舞的阴谋。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "咱们下山吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "下山到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我想到点苍山一行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此去不知能否见一灯神尼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "八剑我只会五剑尚差三剑，唉……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我想……我想……求你一件事……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你……你……能否将那伤心剑说给我听……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你传我那招伤心剑，我用五剑相换。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你……你为什么不躲……你……为什么全不想我一点……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到哪里去，你到哪里去……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你到哪里去？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥！大哥！你回来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，大哥！你可不要再离开你的菊妹……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你抬起头来看着我。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你知不知道，自你离开黑堡，我无日不在思念着你，你的面貌我每天都要想过好几遍……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你想我什么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么来晚了五天，一个也见不着，他们高手较量武技，怎会这么快就解决了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总算没有白跑一趟……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没什么，我去将单子洗了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我去洗了就来。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你受伤了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "傻子！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你昨晚摔痛了？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 133
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "没有，没有，是我昨天实在不该打你，摔了一跤有什么关系，真是说孩子话。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "大哥，你要学伤心剑，我传你好吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "你不再怕对驼叟发的誓言？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我才不信那誓言，只怕咱们……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "愿学！愿学！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那你可要叫我一声师父。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 155
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不成！不成！我是你大哥，怎能叫你师父？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你再不叫我，我就不收你这个徒儿了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "傻子，看你急成那样子，还是叫我菊妹算了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "菊妹，你本来不愿教我，怎么才隔一夜，忽然变得愿意教我？真令大哥想不出是何道理？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你那样对我，我有什么不好教你，咱们彼此间还分什么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "去年受家父之命嫁到胡家，年来我身在胡家仍是念念不忘你，天星明里是我丈夫，其实却不是我的丈夫。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "你当真不知？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "不知。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我和他虽然结过婚，却没有同过房。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "原来你和他有夫妻之名，而无夫妻之实。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "我不能忘你，怎能和他行夫妻之礼。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "其实我对你不好，有什么值得你念念不忘！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "这是命运，我想忘你，想忘也忘不掉，前天夜里你对我那么亲热，这一辈子我更不能忘你了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rui_wei",
      "speaker_name": "芮玮",
      "listener": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "text": "我怎么对你亲热啦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_qiong_ju",
      "speaker_name": "林琼菊",
      "listener": "char_rui_wei",
      "text": "那晚上我失身于你，你还装傻……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 31,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    }
  ],
